## Dough 

The dough recipe is from Frank Pinollo found in the following video:

[![How-To: Make Homemade Pizza with Frank Pinello](https://img.youtube.com/vi/whnvQBhXh3A/0.jpg)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whnvQBhXh3A)

By weights, the recipe is:

- 1000 g all-purpose flour
- 20 g kosher salt
- 10 g extra virgin olive oil
- ???YEAST
- 650 g water 

Yield: 6 dough balls each 270g. 

I started with a recipe that my father found for making pizza

## Sauce

- 28 oz can of whole peeled San Marzano tomatoes
- 1 tbsp of extra virgin olive oil 
- 2 cloves of garlic
- 1 tsp of salt
- ¼ tsp of black pepper 
- ½ tsp of dried oregano
- 1 tsp of dried basil
- ½ tsp of dried majoram 
- 2 tbsp of sugar 

## Cheese

- 100 g low-fat mozzarella
- 10 g white cheddar
- 10 g monterey jack
